OL,3,CThe North Face offers 20% discount if
OL,4,Cyou complete 'racial inclusion' course
OL,6,FThe North Face is offering 20% off to
OL,7,Fcustomers who pass an hour-long online
OL,8,F"racial inclusion" course.
OL,10,FThe American fashion brand is
OL,11,Fpromising to discount purchases for
OL,12,Fthose who complete a four-part digital
OL,13,Fcourse.
OL,15,FTitled "Allyship in the Outdoors", the
OL,16,Fprogramme is aimed at "fostering a
OL,17,Fdeeper understanding" of the "unique
OL,18,Fchallenges that people of colour face
OL,19,Fwhen accessing the outdoors".
