OL,3,CThe North Face offers 20% discount if
OL,4,Cyou complete 'racial inclusion' course
OL,6,FConstructed with the help of UK-based
OL,7,Fconsultancy group Mor Diversity, the
OL,8,Fquestionnaire covers topics such as
OL,9,F"white privilege" and different types
OL,10,Fof racism.
OL,12,FThe start of the course encourages
OL,13,Fpeople to have an open mind "to help
OL,14,Finspire your learning".
OL,16,FIt also urges them to listen to other
OL,17,Fpeople's "lived experiences" and
OL,18,F"commit to being an ally in the
OL,19,Foutdoors".
