OL,3,CThe North Face offers 20% discount if
OL,4,Cyou complete 'racial inclusion' course
OL,6,FCustomers are told the outdoors is for
OL,7,Feveryone.
OL,9,FAs customers progress through the
OL,10,Fcourse their walker climbs higher up
OL,11,Fthe mountain to each module before
OL,12,Freaching the summit.
OL,14,FIn a portion of the course,
OL,15,Fparticipants are told to ask
OL,16,Fthemselves: "How many people of colour
OL,17,Fdo you see on the slopes, the hills
OL,18,Fand the trails?"
