OL,3,CThe North Face offers 20% discount if
OL,4,Cyou complete 'racial inclusion' course
OL,6,FThe brand also mentions the murder of
OL,7,Fin Minneapolis in 2020, which brought
OL,8,Fglobal attention to the Black Lives
OL,9,FMatter movement.
OL,11,FThe section states the incident
OL,12,F"fostered a new awakening in the
OL,13,Foutdoors that racial inclusion and
OL,14,Frepresentation matters in sports like
OL,15,Fclimbing, hiking, snowboarding, skiing
OL,16,Fand trail running".
OL,18,FAt the end of the course, customers
OL,19,Fcan claim their 20 per cent off
OL,20,Fvoucher.
